data.englishTranslation: With the Name of Allah, Allah is the Most Great! (O Allah, from You and to You.) O Allah, accept it from me.
data.transliteration: Bismillaahi wallaahu 'Akbar [Allaahumma minka wa laka] Allaahumma taqabbal minnee.
data.arabicVerse: بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُمَّ مِنْكَ ولَكَ اللَّهُمَّ تَقَبَّلْ مِنِّي
